OL,3,CHow climate change is increasing the
OL,4,Cdangers for British scientists
OL,6,FWords by Senior Producer Rhiannon
OL,7,FHopley
OL,9,FIn Antarctica, the climate is changing
OL,10,Fand so is the way scientists work.
OL,12,FIt is a mountainous landscape and also
OL,13,Fone of the coldest, driest places on
OL,14,Fearth.
OL,16,FThe continent is fraught with threats
OL,17,Ffor scientists working on the ice.
OL,19,FHidden under the snow are crevasses -
OL,20,Fdeep holes in the ice which can go
OL,21,Fdown for dozens of metres.
