OL,3,CHow climate change is increasing the
OL,4,Cdangers for British scientists
OL,6,FThey are hard to see and if you fall
OL,7,Fin one, it can be deadly.
OL,9,FField guides use specialist equipment
OL,10,Fto scan the ice and identify crevasses.
OL,12,FThey mark them with flags to warn
OL,13,Fscientists where to avoid walking.
OL,15,FAs the climate warms, the ice is
OL,16,Fbecoming less stable.
