OL,3,CHow climate change is increasing the
OL,4,Cdangers for British scientists
OL,6,FRainfall, which is becoming more
OL,7,Ffrequent in Antarctica, can flow into
OL,8,Fcracks in the ice. It expands when it
OL,9,Ffreezes making those cracks even
OL,10,Fbigger.
OL,12,FIt means trips by the field guides to
OL,13,Fplot safe passages are needing to take
OL,14,Fplace more frequently.
OL,16,FScientists are also finding routes
OL,17,Fthey used to do on a skidoo are no
OL,18,Flonger strong enough and can only be
OL,19,Fwalked.
