OL,3,CHow climate change is increasing the
OL,4,Cdangers for British scientists
OL,6,FOther changes include sea ice becoming
OL,7,Fweaker. After losing equipment as it
OL,8,Ffell through the ice into the sea,
OL,9,Fsome scientists have now taken to
OL,10,Ftying flotation devices onto their
OL,11,Fbelongings so as not to lose them
OL,12,Faltogether.
OL,14,FIn these changing times, science is
OL,15,Fhaving to change fast to keep up.
